annotationA: Mesencephalic astrocyte-derived neurotrophic factor homolog; Required during the maturation of the embryonic nervous system for maintenance of neuronal and cuticular connectivity. Essential for maintenance of dopaminergic neurons and dopamine levels
annotationB: Glycoprotein 93; ATP binding; unfolded protein binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: protein folding; endodermal digestive tract morphogenesis; response to stress; midgut development
